The code for the previous map:

df$type<-as.factor(df$type)

factpal <- colorFactor(topo.colors(5), df$type)



df %>% leaflet() %>% addTiles() %>% 
        addCircleMarkers(lat = ~lat, lng = ~lng,
                         color = ~factpal(type),
                         label = ~name,
                         clusterOptions = markerClusterOptions()) %>%
        addLegend(pal = factpal, value=~type)
